import React from 'react';
import './buttons.css'
import {useSpring, config,animated } from 'react-spring'
import Styles from './animation' 


export const ButtonPopRight = (long,tall) => {
    const [length, setLength] =useSpring(() => ({width:"13.173"}))
    return (  
        <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="63.63"
            height="59.083"
            version="1.1"
            viewBox="0 0 16.835 15.632"
            >
            <defs>
                <filter
                id="filter973"
                width="1.278"
                height="1.306"
                x="-0.139"
                y="-0.153"
                colorInterpolationFilters="sRGB"
                >
                <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="0.763"></feGaussianBlur>
                </filter>
            </defs>
            <g
                fillOpacity="1"
                strokeWidth="0.008"
                transform="translate(-54.046 -143.913)"
            >
                <animated.rect
                width = {length.width}
                // height="11.97"
                x="55.877"
                y="145.744"
                fill="gray"
                filter="url(#filter973)"
                opacity="0.799"
                rx="5.476"
                ry="5.985"
                style={{ mixBlendMode: "normal" }}
                ></animated.rect>
                {/* <rect
                width="12.131"
                height="11.331"
                x="56.383"
                y="146.041"
                fill="#fff"
                rx="6.065"
                ry="5.666"
                ></rect> */}
            </g>
        </svg>
    );
}
